::Battera::

She stopped, turned and faced CyberShark. She placed her hands on his 
shoulders and looked him square in the eyes.
"OK, Your blue about something.  I don't know what and I don't care.  But I 
am n a happy mood and wish you were too. Now smile and be happy." she said 
with a chuckle. "Because if you don't, I shall pick you up, carry you 
outside and throw you into a lake somewhere and let you cool off that way." 
She was laughing now, "Got it?"

She knew that she couldn't pick him up.  But she hoped it sounded good.
She laughed at her own words for she knew how rediculuos it sounded.  But 
she hoped he would at least smile at it.
